CatDescriptText: The books on the desk are: John Henry by Roark Bradford, Life in Modern America by Kelty, What Makes Sammy Run by Budd Schulberg, The Prospector by Ralph Connor, Corporal Cameron by Ralph Connor, The Lone Ranger and The Gold Robbery by Striker, Robin by Burnett, Captain Blood by Rafael Sabatini, The Seahawk by Rafael Sabatini, and Cart of Many Colors by Meiklejohn.
